      "raw_text": "the trust, though the strike is not\nagainst them.\n\n\nThe trust is managing to worry along\nand deliver its beer. Its breweries\nhave not been brewing any beer since\nthe strike, but they have large sup\nply on hand.\n\n\nMembers of the trades council state\nthat there is no prospect whatever of\na csonflict between the striking unions\nand the bartenders, as the brewery\nwork men do not intend to ask the\nlatter union to strike in sympathy.\n\n\nThe strike was endorsed last night\nby the trades council."
